text: Rowland Fernyhough (born 9 July 1954) is a British equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:British male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Great Britain Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
